reviewText: If you love Robot Chicken, then you'll love the specials as well.  More of the same!
excellent product. I highly recommend this to everyone who needs it and not to those who do not have a need for the item
Must have for Robot Chicken fans
xmas with robot chicken?  what more could you want?
Well I realized that all the specials will end up on one or more of each season DVD's...so I should just return this and get something else.

This is a great DVD!  It gives you every Robot Chicken Christmas related episode!  The only reason I did not give it 5 stars is because the Dragonball Christmas episode is the edited version, and bleeps out all of the colorful language used by Santa!  Every other episode/special on this disc gives you the fully unedited language version.  It makes no sense why they would edit only this episode.
Bought as a present.  DAD loves this show
It's Robot Chicken, what can you say other than it's some funny stuff to see.
